tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE spatial_coordinates (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    object_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    x_coord FLOAT NOT NULL,
    y_coord FLOAT NOT NULL,
    z_coord FLOAT NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE ar_relationships (
    relationship_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    object_id INT,
    tag_id INT,
    FOREIGN KEY (object_id) REFERENCES ar_objects(object_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (tag_id) REFERENCES ar_tags(tag_id)
);
